{"tid":1995892,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【影片】遭遇喬裝警暴力致骨折　治療半年難完全康復 — 林維坤抹不走的傷痕","createTime":"2020-04-30T15:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T16:25:43.000Z","uid":5191,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"359b961e89d2779fd890e45ed9eb387a0ac01f4a","tid":1995892,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"【影片】遭遇喬裝警暴力致骨折　治療半年難完全康復 &mdash; 林維坤抹不走的傷痕<br />\n<br />\n報道全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aSfTkD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aSfTkD&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ0VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=c43483e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3aSfTkD</a><br />\n<br />\n2019 年 8 月 11 日晚上的銅鑼灣街頭，假扮示威者的喬裝警員首次現身作出拘捕，林維坤被推倒制服及毆打，導致左肩一帶最少五處骨折。過去半年，針灸、放血、物理治療已成為林維坤的生活日常。事隔逾八個月，對林維坤而言，康復之路仍然漫長，追究警暴決心未變。"},{"pid":"ff56343b316eac8a1f56afd471db137b7d4a19a0","tid":1995892,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:04:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d6915bb50b239b7ee4e5260241ece56c42432b6","tid":1995892,"uid":82905,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚嬲"},{"pid":"a4dc96fb56debcda8a31da97d206a02809aa23df","tid":1995892,"uid":170019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"推喇喂"},{"pid":"480ab79cfafe2ff5eaa37e68b5bebf6f68d00ae8","tid":1995892,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"Dead body幫手告狗賠錢啦屌"},{"pid":"71618cbaf85fbc1df74adde5050c7f687b923c52","tid":1995892,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:08:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f695a5ca81d4ba3495c4be6c24455a460116d1c3","tid":1995892,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r